<script >
	String.prototype.trim = function () {
		return this.replace(/^\s*/, "").replace(/\s*$/, "");
	}

	//  enable/disable Specialization option based on Physician Type selection
	function updatePhysicianType() {
		var objSpecialists = document.getElementById("rdoDocTypeSpecialist");
		var objddSpecialist = document.getElementById("ddSpecialist");
		var cpsoSpecialzation = document.getElementById("cpsoSpecialzation");
		if (objSpecialists.checked) {
			cpsoSpecialzation.style.display = "block";
			objddSpecialist.disabled = false;
			document.getElementById("lblSpecialization").className = "";
		}
		else {
			cpsoSpecialzation.style.display = "none";
			objddSpecialist.disabled = true;
			objddSpecialist.selectedIndex = 0;
			document.getElementById("lblSpecialization").className = "light-grey";
		}
	}


	//  enable/disable Keyword Search based on Discipline selection
	function updateDisciplinary() {
		var chkPracticeRestrictions = document.getElementById("p_lt_ctl01_pageplaceholder_p_lt_ctl02_CPSO_AllDoctorsSearch_chkPracticeRestrictions");
    	var chkPendingHearings = document.getElementById("p_lt_ctl01_pageplaceholder_p_lt_ctl02_CPSO_AllDoctorsSearch_chkPendingHearings");
    	var chkPastHearings = document.getElementById("p_lt_ctl01_pageplaceholder_p_lt_ctl02_CPSO_AllDoctorsSearch_chkPastHearings");
    	var chkHospitalNotices = document.getElementById("p_lt_ctl01_pageplaceholder_p_lt_ctl02_CPSO_AllDoctorsSearch_chkHospitalNotices");
    	var chkConcerns = document.getElementById("p_lt_ctl01_pageplaceholder_p_lt_ctl02_CPSO_AllDoctorsSearch_chkConcerns");
    	var chkNotices = document.getElementById("p_lt_ctl01_pageplaceholder_p_lt_ctl02_CPSO_AllDoctorsSearch_chkNotices");
    	var txtExtraInfo = document.getElementById("txtExtraInfo");

    	if (chkPracticeRestrictions.checked || chkPendingHearings.checked || chkPastHearings.checked || chkHospitalNotices.checked || chkConcerns.checked || chkNotices.checked) {
    		txtExtraInfo.disabled = false;
    	}
    	else {
    		txtExtraInfo.disabled = true;
    		txtExtraInfo.value = "";
    	}
    }



    //  enable/disable FirstName textfield if value exists in firstName
    function updateFirstName() {
    	var objLastName = document.getElementById("txtLastName");
    	var objFirstName = document.getElementById("txtFirstName");

    	if (objLastName.value.trim().length > 0) {
    		objFirstName.disabled = false;
    	}
    }

    //  enable/disable FirstName textfield if value exists in firstName
    function emptyFirstName(objLastName, objFirstName) {
    	if (objLastName.value.trim().length == 0) {
    		objFirstName.disabled = true;
    		objFirstName.value = "";
    	}
    }

</script>
